COMUNICACIÓN CON EL SERVIDOR

- AJAX 
  -> Context / Call Stack
  -> Event Loop / Pila / Cua
  -> Callback 

- XMLHTTPREQUEST
  -> open / send
  -> .readyState / status / onreadystatechange / responseText
  -> FormData 
  -> Convertir a JSON : JSON.stringify(Object.fromEntries(formData));
  -> XHR : 
      · makeRequest / open / onload / oncomplete / onerror / send / 
      · request / response 
  -> Api : 
    · GET / PUT / DELETE / POST / PATCH

- PROMISES
  -> new Promise( resolve , reject ) => { } .then / .catch  /*Sino es una cosa es la otra*/

- FETCH 
  -> fetch : localizacion JSON 
  -> response.status : estat de descarrega / response.json() : transforma json a Objecte

- ASYNC AWAIT
  -> async function 
          await fetch ( json )
          await response.json()
          